long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Seamlessly scrape essential business information from Proff websites across Norway, Sweden, Finland, and Denmark.

✨ One-Click Magic:
Export leads from Proff websites to CSV, Excel, or JSON with just one click!

📞 Generate Potential Leads:
Easily extract business phone numbers, mobile phones, and work emails to connect with potential clients! 📧

🎯 Targeted Searches:
Easily filter by county, municipality, or even specific industries to find exactly what you need!

✅ GDPR Compliant:
Rest assured, we only collect publicly available data—100% compliant with GDPR!

🔒 Local Data Handling:
Keep your data safe and secure on your device—no cloud storage worries!

🤔 FAQs
Got questions? Check out our FAQ section for quick answers!

🛠️ More Nordic Leads Tools
Click the tool menu to discovery more lead tools.

📩 Feedback
We’re here to help! Reach out to us at help@niomaker.com for any inquiries or feedback.
